Implemented API to return service categories.

Modified: GET /api/v1/services
- include location name and ID for each service
- include service category name and ID

Modified: GET /api/v1/services/<service_id>
- include upvotes in each service review
- include location name and ID for each service
- include service category name and ID

Modified: GET /api/v1/serviceProviders/<sp_id>/services/<service_id>
- include upvotes in each service review
- include location name and ID for each service
- include service category name and ID

New API: GET /api/v1/serviceCategories
- returns all available service category names and IDs
